{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/CS/Gatsby/utterances/","result":{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"totalCount":31},"markdownRemark":{"id":"429976b2-5875-5b99-bb89-96495f9f7218","html":"<h2>깃허브 이슈로 댓글을 관리하는 utterances</h2>\n<p>🔮 utterances는 댓글을 깃허브 이슈로 관리하는 위젯이다. utterances를 깃허브 르포에 설치하면 <code>utterances-bot</code>이 모든 페이지를 방문하여 댓글이 있는 페이지마다 이슈를 생성한 뒤 댓글을 그 이슈에 추가한다. 즉 utterances 댓글을 다는 행위는 이슈를 추가하거나 이슈 내에 글을 추가하는 것과 같으므로, 댓글 작성에 깃허브 계정이 필요하다.</p>\n<br>\n<h3>1. <a href=\"https://github.com/apps/utterances\">utterances app</a> 을 댓글을 관리할 르포에 설치한다.</h3>\n<p>이때 르포는 <code>public</code>이어야 한다. 이 블로그의 경우, 깃허브 페이지를 호스팅하는 <code>nearnear.github.io</code> 르포에 앱을 설치했지만, 만약 페이지가 공개되어 있지 않다면 별도의 르포를 생성하여 연동할 수 있다. 별도의 르포를 생성하면 댓글과 블로그 글을 따로 관리할 수 있다.</p>\n<br>\n<h3>2. <a href=\"https://utteranc.es/\">utteranc.es</a> 에서 config를 선택하고 <code>&#x3C;script></code> 태그를 활용한 코드를 얻는다.</h3>\n<p>대략 다음과 같은 코드를 얻을 수 있다. <code>&#x3C;script></code> 태그는 HTML에서 외부 스크립트를 불러올 수 있게한다.</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container abyss\" data-language=\"html\" data-index=\"0\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">&lt;</span><span class=\"mtk7\">script</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk6\">src</span><span class=\"mtk1\">=</span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;https://utteranc.es/client.js&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">       </span><span class=\"mtk6\">repo</span><span class=\"mtk1\">=</span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;nearnear/nearnear.github.io&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">       </span><span class=\"mtk6\">issue-term</span><span class=\"mtk1\">=</span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;pathname&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">       </span><span class=\"mtk6\">label</span><span class=\"mtk1\">=</span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;comments&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">       </span><span class=\"mtk6\">theme</span><span class=\"mtk1\">=</span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;github-light&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">       </span><span class=\"mtk6\">crossorigin</span><span class=\"mtk1\">=</span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;anonymous&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">       </span><span class=\"mtk6\">async</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk7\">script</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>그러나 React는 보안 이슈로 <code>&#x3C;script></code> 태그를 허용하지 않는다. 이를 허용하도록 설정할 수 있지만, 대신 여기서는 새로운 컴포넌트를 작성해서 원하는 바를 달성했다.</p>\n<br>\n<h3>3. <code>/src/components/comments</code> 폴더를 생성하고 <code>index.js</code> 추가한다.</h3>\n<p>이 경로는 Gatsby 프로젝트에 따라 다를 것이다. 대체적으로 <code>/src/components</code> 내에 <code>comments.js</code> 컴포넌트를 작성하는 것으로 생각할 수 있다.</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container abyss\" data-language=\"js\" data-index=\"1\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk7\">import</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> React, { useEffect } </span><span class=\"mtk7\">from</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;react&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk15 mtki\">const</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> COMMENTS_ID </span><span class=\"mtk7\">=</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;comments-container&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk15 mtki\">const</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk6\">Comments</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk7\">=</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> () </span><span class=\"mtk15 mtki\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> {</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk6\">useEffect</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(() </span><span class=\"mtk15 mtki\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> {    </span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"mtk15 mtki\">const</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> script </span><span class=\"mtk7\">=</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> document.</span><span class=\"mtk6\">createElement</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;script&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">);</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    script.src </span><span class=\"mtk7\">=</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;https://utteranc.es/client.js&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    script.</span><span class=\"mtk6\">setAttribute</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;repo&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">, </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;nearnear/nearnear.github.io&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">);</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    script.</span><span class=\"mtk6\">setAttribute</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;issue-term&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">, </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;pathname&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">);</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    script.</span><span class=\"mtk6\">setAttribute</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;crossorigin&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">, </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;anonymous&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">);</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    script.async </span><span class=\"mtk7\">=</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk4\">true</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">      </span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"mtk15 mtki\">const</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> comments </span><span class=\"mtk7\">=</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> document.</span><span class=\"mtk6\">getElementById</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(COMMENTS_ID);</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"mtk7\">if</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> (comments) comments.</span><span class=\"mtk6\">appendChild</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(script);</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">      </span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"mtk7\">return</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> () </span><span class=\"mtk15 mtki\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> {</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">      </span><span class=\"mtk15 mtki\">const</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> comments </span><span class=\"mtk7\">=</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> document.</span><span class=\"mtk6\">getElementById</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(COMMENTS_ID);</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">      </span><span class=\"mtk7\">if</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> (comments) comments.innerHTML </span><span class=\"mtk7\">=</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    };</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  }, []);</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk7\">return</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> (</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    &lt;</span><span class=\"mtk7\">div</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk6\">id</span><span class=\"mtk7\">=</span><span class=\"mtk1\">{COMMENTS_ID} /&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  );</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">};</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk7\">export</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk7\">default</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> Comments;</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><code>script</code>를 요소로 생성한 뒤 <code>.setAttribute</code>를 통해 config 값을 입력했다.</p>\n<br>\n<h3>4. <code>/src/templates</code>의 <code>blog-post.js</code>에 <code>&#x3C;Comments /></code>를 추가한다.</h3>\n<p>이 경로 또한 프로젝트에 따라 다를 것이나, <code>/src/template/</code> 의 파일에 추가하는 것으로 생각하자.</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container abyss\" data-language=\"js\" data-index=\"2\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk7\">...</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk3\">// reference utterances</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk7\">import</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> Comments </span><span class=\"mtk7\">from</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;../components/comments&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk15 mtki\">const</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk6\">BlogPost</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk7\">=</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> ({ </span><span class=\"mtk19 mtki\">data</span><span class=\"mtk1\">, </span><span class=\"mtk19 mtki\">pageContext</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> }) </span><span class=\"mtk15 mtki\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> {</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk15 mtki\">const</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> { markdownRemark, allMarkdownRemark } </span><span class=\"mtk7\">=</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> data;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk15 mtki\">const</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> { frontmatter, html } </span><span class=\"mtk7\">=</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> markdownRemark;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk15 mtki\">const</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> { handleSelect, selectedCategory } </span><span class=\"mtk7\">=</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk6\">useCategory</span><span class=\"mtk1\">();</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk15 mtki\">const</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> { currentPage, handlePageChange } </span><span class=\"mtk7\">=</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk6\">usePagination</span><span class=\"mtk1\">({</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    totalCount: allMarkdownRemark.totalCount,</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    siblingCount: PAGE.SIBLINGCOUNT,</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    pageSize: PAGE.PAGESIZE,</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  });</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk7\">return</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> (</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    &lt;</span><span class=\"mtk15 mtki\">Layout</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">      </span><span class=\"mtk6\">handlePageChange</span><span class=\"mtk7\">=</span><span class=\"mtk1\">{handlePageChange}</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">      </span><span class=\"mtk6\">handleSelect</span><span class=\"mtk7\">=</span><span class=\"mtk1\">{handleSelect}</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">      </span><span class=\"mtk6\">selectedCategory</span><span class=\"mtk7\">=</span><span class=\"mtk1\">{selectedCategory}</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">      </span><span class=\"mtk6\">currentPage</span><span class=\"mtk7\">=</span><span class=\"mtk1\">{currentPage}</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    &gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">      &lt;</span><span class=\"mtk7\">div</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk6\">className</span><span class=\"mtk7\">=</span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;templateContainer&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">        &lt;</span><span class=\"mtk15 mtki\">PostHeader</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk6\">data</span><span class=\"mtk7\">=</span><span class=\"mtk1\">{frontmatter} /&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">        &lt;</span><span class=\"mtk15 mtki\">PostContent</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk6\">content</span><span class=\"mtk7\">=</span><span class=\"mtk1\">{html} /&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">        &lt;</span><span class=\"mtk15 mtki\">PostNavigation</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">          </span><span class=\"mtk6\">data</span><span class=\"mtk7\">=</span><span class=\"mtk1\">{pageContext}</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">          </span><span class=\"mtk6\">selectedCategory</span><span class=\"mtk7\">=</span><span class=\"mtk1\">{selectedCategory}</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">        /&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">        &lt;</span><span class=\"mtk7\">hr</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> /&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"g